						               													<description>Come along and enjoy the fun! In Perfect Holiday you and your family are on vacation and you compete against other players to have the best time ever. Set your goals, buy tickets, visit locations, and plan your trip around this perfect resort island! Earn points by carrying out activities and by completing tours in 6 rounds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this set collection game, you try to collect as many activity cards as possible. You score bonus points for activities in the same colour, and you can also score points for making selfies, but only if you have made a selfie in at least four locations. Every round you have 5 action points you can use to:&amp;#10;1. travel between locations;&amp;#10;2. do a one-day activity;&amp;#10;3. start a multiple day activity;&amp;#10;4. completing a multiple day activity;&amp;#10;5. taking a selfie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Some activities cost money, which you can get at the hotel. But beware, there are also event cards that can ruin your plans: it might be too hot to do everything you planned, or it is raining cats and dogs and you have to stay inside.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who scores the most points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
